  <summary date="2021-04-29T15:38:39Z" status="Introduced in House">21st Century NICS Act

This bill modifies procedures for conducting firearms-related background checks through the national instant criminal background check system (NICS).

Specifically, it permits the NICS to query an additional database&#8212;the National Data Exchange&#8212;as part of a firearm-related background check.</summary>
